commit.message:
Remove if in DICTIONARYWDFLT

Variables are in all DXFs where is DICTIONARYWDFLT object.

Fix DICTIONARYWDFLT object

In R13, R14, R2000 DWG files is same structure.
Add logging of ATTDEF flags in R14
Log mlinestyle flag
Log style FLAG

encode: convert xdata TV from utf8 also

Fixes GH #873

bits: convert TV from utf8 back to codepage

when imported from JSON. Fixes GH #873

Fix spaces in logging of SPLINE scenario

Actually:
scenario: 2 [BL 0]
         BEZIER(0x2)

After:
scenario: 2 [BL 0]
          BEZIER(0x2)
Log LTYPE shape flag
Fix ltype dashes on R13
Improve logging of text dashes

dwg_api: relax invalid name checks

only warn, no error
dwg_is_valid_name_u8: less code

codepages: add is_valid_name u8 API and tests

with the u8 and native API.
add and in_json needs u8, the rest native.
single and multibyte, TV and TU.

codepages: add dwg_codepage_isalnum

for all the codepages.
except utf8, utf16 which falls back to iswalnum().
we really dont want to switch locale back and forth just to
use the broken system libc isalnum() api.
at least windows would have a is*_l variant.

for chars under 128 we just refer to libc isalnum(), and our alnum
tables ignore them.

Fixes GH #958
gh: fix sanitizer issue

gh: skip broken sanitize run-time for a while

See https://github.com/actions/runner-images/issues/9491

gh: sanitize with -O1, use contains

substring checks.
oda: update to 25.1

GTAGS: add gtags.files

for a much smaller proper GPATH file

bits: fix bit_utf8_to_TU

off-by-one, and no test coverage!
Fixes GH #959
